casebody.data:
No. 10-1007. Kentucky, Petitioner v. Reyes Velasquez. 564 U.S. 1032, 131 S. Ct. 3082,

180 L. Ed. 2d 881,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4921. June 27, 2011.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeals of Kentucky. Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Court of Appeals of Kentucky for further consideration in light of Davis v. United States, 564 U.S. 229, 131 S. Ct. 2419, 180 L. Ed. 2d 285 (2011).
